---
title: One-Pan Spicy Carolina BBQ Chicken Tacos with Creamy Slaw
description: Carolina BBQ is known for the spicy, mustard-spike sauce that tops slow-cooked, pulled meat. These tacos aren’t just about the BBQ though: you’ll add pickled jalapeño, crispy fried onion, and a creamy slaw. The best part? This taco night takes just 15-minutes to get to your plate, and only a few more seconds to get into your belly!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/spicy-carolina-bbq-pulled-chicken-tacos-ced51473.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/one-pan-spicy-carolina-bbq-chicken-tacos-61670dd477e3bd0089465a9a-364b017a.pdf
course: main course
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/one-pan-spicy-carolina-bbq-chicken-tacos-61670dd477e3bd0089465a9a
time required: 15 minutes
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
cuisine: North America
nutrition:
  calories: 750 kcal
  fat: 30 g
  saturated fat: 13 g
